    <item>
      <title>what to show</title>
      <link>https://shedshow.art/what-to-show/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://shedshow.art/what-to-show/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;show something good. show something bad. show something unfinished. show something you&amp;rsquo;ve never shown before. show something you hate. show something you made today. show something you made tomorrow. show something weird. show something made of your favorite color. show something loud. show something hot. show something you may never show again. show something you need to talk about. show something you&amp;rsquo;re scared to talk about. show something that motivates you to make more. show something you love. show something you&amp;rsquo;re okay with tossing out right after. show something that makes you think about something you love to think about. show something old. show something still. show something in a medium you haven&amp;rsquo;t worked in. show something raw. show something at SHED SHOW.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
